{"tid":2227911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞全港賣旗日就得，搞選舉遊行就唔得，原來防疫措施只防【選舉遊行】！！！","createTime":"2020-10-03T07:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T07:43:18.000Z","uid":244704,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57a2631e032d39ba2dfda71977e27bfca22a28c0","tid":2227911,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"全港賣旗日<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  社會福利署（社署）發言人表示，基督教靈實協會獲發公開籌款許可證在今日（十月三日）由上午七時至下午十二時三十分，進行全港賣旗活動。<br />\n<br />\n  所有獲發許可證於<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>公眾地方</strong></span></span>進行的慈善籌款活動詳情，包括任何更新的資料，已透過香港政府一站通網頁（<a href=\"http://www.gov.hk/tc/theme/fundraising/search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ftheme%2Ffundraising%2Fsearch&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=e822cb4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.gov.hk/tc/theme/fundraising/search</a> ） 發布，而賣旗日許可證亦已上載至社署網頁（<a href=\"http://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_controlofc/sub_flagdays\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_pubsvc%2Fpage_controlofc%2Fsub_flagdays&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=0f1bde87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_controlofc/sub_flagdays</a> ），以供查閱賣旗機構的聯絡方法及已獲准舉行的賣旗日活動資料。市民如有其他查詢，可致電社署熱線2343 2255，或1823電話中心專線3142 2678。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人補充說：「市民如對賣旗活動有所懷疑，請不要捐助，並立即通知警方。」<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年10月3日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間6時00分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/03/P2020093000257.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202010%2F03%2FP2020093000257.htm&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=b2612222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/03/P2020093000257.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2115e065d804f6b9d2dd608792a6c5c0a291e87b","tid":2227911,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedB